        title=\"java_lang\"\n        src=\"/static/fde3743516de00474b1427e24c628e7d/fcb94/java_lang.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fde3743516de00474b1427e24c628e7d/5a46d/java_lang.png 300w,\n/static/fde3743516de00474b1427e24c628e7d/fcb94/java_lang.png 452w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color: #888888; font-size: 12px;\">\n  https://docstore.mik.ua/orelly/java-ent/jnut/ch12_01.htm\n</p>\n<p>별도의 import 없어도 사용할 수 있는\n자바의 기본적인 클래스들을 포함한다.\n모든 클래스의 조상인 Object 클래스,\nString 클래스, 각종 Wrapper 클래스 등..</p>\n<p>공식 문서를 보며 다음 내용들을 찾아보자.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Object</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">String</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">StringBuffer</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">StringBuilder</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Math</code> 클래스</li>\n<li>각종 Wrapper 클래스</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Object</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">String</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">StringBuffer</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">StringBuilder</code>,\n<code class=\"language-text\">Math</code>, 그리고 각종 Wrapper 클래스 등에 대해 알아보자.</p>\n<h2 id=\"javautil-패키지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javautil-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"javautil 패키지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>java.util 패키지</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 502px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 124%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"java_util\"\n        title=\"java_util\"\n        src=\"/static/4d90a4de1f42ec60cf2827afaa39164a/eea79/java_util.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d90a4de1f42ec60cf2827afaa39164a/5a46d/java_util.png 300w,\n/static/4d90a4de1f42ec60cf2827afaa39164a/eea79/java_util.png 502w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 502px) 100vw, 502px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color: #888888; font-size: 12px;\">\n  http://web.deu.edu.tr/doc/oreily/java/fclass/ch17_js.htm\n</p>\n<p>Collections 프레임워크, 이벤트 모델,\n날짜와 시간 관련 메서드와\n각종 유틸리티 클래스들을 담고 있다.</p>\n<p>공식 문서를 보며 다음 내용들을 찾아보자.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Objects</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Random</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">regex</code> 패키지</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Scanner</code> 클래스</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">StringTokenizer</code> 클래스</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"javamath-패키지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javamath-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"javamath 패키지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>java.math 패키지</h2>\n<p>더 크고 정밀한 수를 다루기 위한\nBigInteger와 BigDecimal 클래스를 제공한다.\n공식 문서를 찾아보자.</p>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>남궁성, Java의 정석 (3rd Edition), 도우출판</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/index.html\">Java SE 8 Documentation - Oracle</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"유용한 패키지","date":"December 24, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Java/211224-useful-packages/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Java/211223-exception-handling/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"예외 처리"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}